data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Miramar, Florida! This lakefront one-story villa is a corner unit and it has a 1-car garage and a screened-in patio. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence provides a spacious and well-designed layout. Open living space, featuring high ceilings and ample natural light that accentuates the neutral tones throughout. Located in the desirable city of Miramar, you'll find yourself in a community that combines convenience with a suburban atmosphere. Nearby amenities includes pool, tennis, basketball. Shopping, parks, excellent schools, makes it an ideal location for families and individuals alike. Don't miss the opportunity to make this villa your new home. Schedule a viewing today and discover the epitome of comfortable living in Miramar, FL.
